        <h4 class="title">Warning signs of stroke </h4>

        <ul class="bullet-list">
            <li class="list">Sudden feeling of weakness, numbness, or loss of feeling in the hands, feet, or face,
                especially on one side of the body. </li>
            <li class="list">Suddenly speaking unclearly or having difficulty speaking, or having difficulty
                understanding what others are saying. </li>
            <li class="list">Experience blurry or double vision in one or both eyes. </li>
            <li class="list">Sudden and unexplained severe dizziness, unsteadiness, loss of balance or movement
                disorder. </li>
            <li class="list">A sudden and unusual headache. </li>
        </ul>
